==English==
===Etymology===
Former trademark of Wham-O, which introduced the product in 1958

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /huːla 'huːp/

===Noun===
'''hula hoop'''

# A [[toy]] in the form of a large [[hoop]] which is [[twirl]]ed around various parts of the body, especially the [[waist]].

